snippet.textDisplay: Beautifully rendered by great musicians and amazing job by Shaan....reading some of the comments below...it is a shame people become so personal and enraged by each other's comments...we all come from the same place originally and must respect each other despite our differences....as human beings....music is about universal love...that is the greatest  message these talented people gift us with when they sing with their hearts and souls so profoundly...so that we can share in spirit some common ground that goes beyond history, politics, race and religion....music is the core of love for mankind....
